phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common Room+ViewModel mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Blocking calls | Use Flow |
| No suspend | Use suspend |
| No error handling | Use try-catch |
| Tight coupling | Use Repository |
| No caching | Cache data |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Use Flow
fun getNotes(): Flow<List<Note>> = dao.getAllNotes()

// 2. Use suspend
suspend fun addNote(note: Note) = dao.insertNote(note)

// 3. Handle errors
try {
    dao.deleteNote(id)
} catch (e: Exception) {
    // Handle
}

// 4. Use Repository
class NoteRepository(private val dao: NoteDao)

// 5. Cache in Repository
private var cache: List<Note>? = null

// 6. Offline support
// Repository handles both local and remote
```
